WEBVTT

00:00.467 --> 00:01.934
MAN: <i>Previously on</i> Underground...

00:02.001 --> 00:03.737
We're here to begin
construction on your nursery.

00:03.804 --> 00:05.538
- My name's Clyde and this is...
- Hollander!

00:05.604 --> 00:07.439
- JOHN: <i> What happened?</i>
- HOLLANDER: <i> Risdin...</i>

00:07.505 --> 00:08.707
They got Clyde.

00:08.774 --> 00:10.809
Inside each of us, there's two wolves...

00:10.876 --> 00:12.973
<i> ...and the good wolf lives on love.</i>

00:13.040 --> 00:14.881
Is Pa the good or the bad wolf?

00:14.947 --> 00:17.283
If you were mine, I would
protect you, no matter what.

00:17.349 --> 00:18.918
I'd protect your secrets, too.

00:18.985 --> 00:21.053
(GASPING)

00:21.120 --> 00:22.454
JEREMIAH: We got one of yours!

00:22.521 --> 00:24.957
- (ROSALEE SCREAMS)
- Wait, wait, wait, wait.

00:25.023 --> 00:27.126
We ain't no help to her
if we get caught, too.

00:31.563 --> 00:35.334
<i> ♪ How am I supposed to survive?</i>

00:35.401 --> 00:36.836
(HOOVES CLOPPING)

00:36.901 --> 00:41.355
<i> ♪ If I don't know what's wrong
and what's right? ♪</i>

00:42.441 --> 00:47.679
<i> ♪ How am I supposed to know freedom? ♪</i>

00:47.746 --> 00:51.995
<i> ♪ If I don't know I'm living inside? ♪</i>

00:53.151 --> 00:57.325
<i> ♪ 'Cause you've got
the nail to my all ♪</i>

00:58.356 --> 01:02.616
<i> ♪ My only chance to know what is what ♪</i>

01:03.895 --> 01:09.335
<i> ♪ 'Cause you've got
the nail to my all ♪</i>

01:09.401 --> 01:13.439
<i> ♪ An object I can't even control ♪</i>

01:13.505 --> 01:17.243
<i> ♪ Set me free ♪</i>

01:18.510 --> 01:22.314
<i> ♪ Pull the nail out with your teeth ♪</i>

01:22.380 --> 01:24.683
(GROANING)

01:24.749 --> 01:26.885
<i> ♪ Set me free ♪</i>

01:26.953 --> 01:29.456
(ROSALEE SCREAMS)

01:29.522 --> 01:32.892
<i> ♪ Don't leave me wasted ♪</i>

01:32.959 --> 01:34.660
(GRUNTING)

01:35.528 --> 01:36.914
<i> ♪ Set me free... ♪</i>

01:36.981 --> 01:39.165
That's a white
woman's dress! Take it off!

01:39.231 --> 01:40.365
(GRUNTS)

01:40.433 --> 01:42.635
<i> ♪ Don't leave me wasted... ♪</i>

01:42.701 --> 01:44.670
- (ROSALEE SCREAMS)
- That's enough!

01:44.737 --> 01:47.040
(GASPING)

01:48.507 --> 01:50.109
That girl's another man's property.

01:52.811 --> 01:55.281
And I plan on bringing her back intact.

